dc_description_s: This polygon data layer represents zoning for St. Croix County, Wisconsin in 2013. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, St_Croix_Zoning_2013.gdb. [County Zoning. The zoning districts are Residence, Agricultural, Agricultural Two, Agricultural Residential, Conservancy, Restricted Commercial, Commercial, and Industrial]
uw_supplemental_s: This metadata was updated to reflect that the data is no longer restricted and has been opened for public use. Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.
